{
  "texts": [
    "It is worth noting that, thanks to ATLA's ease of optimization, our experiments adapt ATLA to study more than 250 adversarial suffixes per victim LLM.",
    "We collect the token level's NLL loss from 50 different target responses from LLAMA2-7B-CHAT.",
    "For all (token, loss) pairs, we rank the tokens according to the loss values, and visualize the first 25 tokens with highest loss (aka also highest weights in ATLA L e).",
    "(Full figure see Fig. 10).",
    "Gradient optimization-based attack methods have been proposed to atatck an LLM by learning an adversarial suffix X."
  ]
}